high_descs: Turn to the left and walk forward to face the dresser.
Pick up the pencil on the dresser.
Step to the left and look up to face a bowl on a shelf.
Place the pencil in the bowl on the shelf.
Pick up the bowl with a pencil in it.
Turn around and walk forward and then face the table on the right.
Place the bowl with a pencil in it on the left side of the table.
anns.task_desc: To put a pencil in a bowl as well as move it to the left side of the computer table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the dresser.
Pick up the pencil closest to the alarm clock.
Take step to the left to face the bowl on the shelf above the lamp.
Place the pencil in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the pencil.
Turn around and head towards the computer desk.
Place the bowl to the left of the book on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place the bowl with a pencil next to the book on the white desk.

high_descs: Turn to the left to see the dresser.
Pick up the pencil from the of the dresser, closer to the middle.
Move a few steps the the left to stay looking at the dresser.
Look above the desk and place the pencil in the bowl.
Take down the bowl from the shelf.
Carry the bowl and turn around, then face the white desk on the right.
Place the bowl on the left side of the white desk.
anns.task_desc: Move a pencil and bowl to a different desk.
